==Swedish==
===Noun===
{{sv-noun-n-zero}}
'''vykort'''

#[[postcard]], in particular with an image on the front side

====Etymology====
From the 1880's, originally "[[brefkort]] [[med]] [[vyer]]" as the first postcards were called "[[brefkort]]" (''letter-card''; modern spelling "[[brevkort]]") but were without any images